---
title: Moroccan Apricot Tofu with Couscous and Yogurt Sauce
description: This meal has a warming balance of sweet, spicy North African-inspired flavours. Fruity apricot and Moroccan spices coat tofu strips in a sticky sauce, while a dollop of creamy yogurt sauce to cool it all down.
